'From Squeak2.9alpha of 12 June 2000 [latest update: #2569] on 5 September 2000 at 10:21:25 pm'!"Change Set:		FixCurveGribbliesDate:			5 September 2000Author:			Dan IngallsFixes a bug that has been present for a looong time, causing gribblies to appear if you move a curve after showing its handles.  Added a call to layoutChanged in CurveMorph>>addHandles."!!CurveMorph methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'di 9/5/2000 22:14'!addHandles	super addHandles.	self updateHandles.	self layoutChanged; changed! !